## Usage

These URLs are now used in `index.html` as the primary image sources. The local `public/images/` files remain as backups.

## Notes

- GitHub generates these complex URLs with JWT tokens for security
- These URLs are permanent and will work as long as the GitHub issue exists
- Total size uploaded: ~4.4 MB (all images combined)
- The URLs include authentication tokens that expire periodically, so they may need to be refreshed
